<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="479" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="3.[831,1437,400,1180]" pageId="3" pageNumber="479">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[831,952,401,425]" pageId="3" pageNumber="479">Diagnosis:</emphasis>
The yellow ground colour distinguishes 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Bassi" authorityYear="2021" box="[831,1006,432,456]" class="Insecta" family="Crambidae" genus="Afrocharltona" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="479" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="oblongissima">
<emphasis box="[831,1006,432,456]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="479">A. oblongissima</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Bassi" authorityYear="2021" box="[1077,1195,432,456]" class="Insecta" family="Crambidae" genus="Afrocharltona" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="479" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="katanga">
<emphasis box="[1077,1195,432,456]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="479">A. katanga</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
described below. The male genitalia are similar to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Bassi" authorityYear="2021" box="[1158,1278,464,488]" class="Insecta" family="Crambidae" genus="Afrocharltona" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="479" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="katanga">
<emphasis box="[1158,1278,464,488]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="479">A. katanga</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
but the valva and apical thorn of the costal arm are longer and the phallus is without cornuti in the vesica. The female genitalia with lateral extension of medium length and thickness, with ductus seminalis originating nearby from ductus bursae are unlike every other species of the 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Bassi &amp; Trematerra" baseAuthorityYear="2014" box="[831,966,657,681]" class="Insecta" family="Crambidae" genus="Ancylolomia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="479" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[831,966,657,681]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="479">Ancylolomia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
complex.
</paragraph>
